room_title: Escape room "The Search for the Jade Skull" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms in Princeton
review: Friends and I did Jade Skull room last Saturday 4/21. Amazing experience! Great room with fun challenging puzzles, awesome surprises and a helpful host. Have done about 20 different rooms and this is definitely one of the top ranking. So much detail we were fully immersed looking forward to trying the other room!
